title: KCRW.com - Top Tunes June 2008
description:
Collected from KCRW.com as their free daily download in the month of June.  MP3 format, 128 Kbps, 44KHz.  Files are uniformly named with embedded album covers and M3U playlist.

If you like what you hear, I strongly urge you to join KCRW as a member or donate to the station (KCRW.com or at 89.9 FM in the LA area).  Enjoy!
